        Use our website to engage in any harmful or illegal activities.
      </li>
      <li class="text-fog text-base">
        Upload, share, or distribute any content that is harmful, offensive, or
        infringing on the rights of others.
      </li>
    </ul>

    <AdUnit client:load slot="6496606373" />

    <h2 class="font-bold text-elba text-lg">3. Content Ownership</h2>
    <p class="text-fog text-base">
      All content, including text, images, videos, articles, training plans, and
      other materials on “tr3,” is owned or licensed by us and is protected by
      copyright and other intellectual property laws. You may not use,
      reproduce, distribute, or modify our content without our express written
      permission.
    </p>

    <h2 class="font-bold text-elba text-lg">4. User-Generated Content</h2>
    <p class="text-fog text-base">
      We may allow users to submit comments, reviews, race reports, or other
      content to our website. By submitting content, you grant us a
      non-exclusive, royalty-free, worldwide, perpetual license to use, modify,
      and display the content on “tr3” and related platforms. You are solely
