      is defamatory, illegal, or infringing on third-party rights.
    </p>

    <h2 class="font-bold text-elba text-lg">5. Disclaimer</h2>
    <p class="text-fog text-base">
      The information provided on “tr3” is for informational purposes only and
      is not a substitute for professional medical advice, diagnosis, or
      treatment. We make no representations or warranties about the accuracy,
      completeness, or suitability of the content for any purpose. You use our
      website and its content at your own risk.
    </p>

    <h2 class="font-bold text-elba text-lg">
      6. Links to Third-Party Websites
    </h2>
    <p class="text-fog text-base">
      Our website may contain links to third-party websites. These links are
      provided for your convenience, and we do not endorse or control the
      content on third-party sites. We are not responsible for the content or
      practices of these external websites.
    </p>

    <h2 class="font-bold text-elba text-lg">7. Privacy</h2>
    <p class="text-fog text-base">
      Your use of “tr3” is subject to our Privacy Policy, which outlines how we
      collect, use, and protect your personal information. By using our website,
      you consent to our data practices as described in the Privacy Policy.
    </p>

    <h2 class="font-bold text-elba text-lg">8. Changes to Terms of Use</h2>
    <p class="text-fog text-base">
      We may update these Terms of Use from time to time to reflect changes in
      our practices or for other operational, legal, or regulatory reasons. We
      will notify you of any material changes by posting the updated Terms of
      Use on this page.
    </p>

    <AdUnit client:load slot="6496606373" />

    <h2 class="font-bold text-elba text-lg">9. Contact Us</h2>
    <p class="text-fog text-base">
      If you have any questions or concerns about these Terms of Use or our
      website, please contact us adam-mckenna@outlook.com.
    </p>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
